{# default Sliding pagination control implementation #}


{# 分页Bundle 默认使用的分页条模板 (可适当的进行修改) #}


{% if pageCount > 1 %}
<div class="pagination">
    {% if first is defined and current != first %}
        <span class="first">
            <a href="{{ path(route, query|merge({(pageParameterName): first})) }}">首页</a>
        </span>
    {% endif %}

    {% if previous is defined %}
        <span class="previous">
            <a href="{{ path(route, query|merge({(pageParameterName): previous})) }}">上一页</a>
        </span>
    {% endif %}

    {% for page in pagesInRange %}
        {% if page != current %}
            <span class="page">
                <a href="{{ path(route, query|merge({(pageParameterName): page})) }}">{{ page }}</a>
            </span>
        {% else %}
            <span class="current">{{ page }}</span>
        {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

    {% if next is defined %}
        <span class="next">
            <a href="{{ path(route, query|merge({(pageParameterName): next})) }}">下一页</a>
        </span>
    {% endif %}

    {% if last is defined and current != last %}
        <span class="last">
            <a href="{{ path(route, query|merge({(pageParameterName): last})) }}">尾页</a>
        </span>
    {% endif %}
</div>
{% endif %}
